        {
          "_name": "article04",
          "_sourceTheme": "paintm5",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".content-wrapper": {
              "padding": "10px",
              "border-top": "10px solid @line",
              "box-shadow": "0 19px 45px 0 #0000001a",
              "background-color": "@cardBg",
              ".content-wrap": {
                "padding": "40px 40px 50px",
                "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                  "padding": "10px 10px 30px"
                },
                ".mbr-section-title": {
                  "margin-bottom": "20px"
                },
                ".text-wrapper": {
                  ".mbr-text": {
                    "display": "inline-block",
                    "width": "80%",
                    "margin-bottom": "0",
                    "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                      "width": "100%"
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".image-wrapper": {
              "display": "grid",
              "grid-template-columns": "1fr 1fr",
              "gap": "10px",
              "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                "grid-template-columns": "1fr"
              },
              ".image-wrap": {
                "img": {
                  "height": "430px",
                  "object-fit": "cover",
                  "@media (max-width: 992px)": {
                    "height": "300px"
                  }
                }
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000c3f"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "color": "#000c3f"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .text-wrapper": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article04 paintm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Line Color\" value=\"#000000\" name=\"line\" selected>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Card BG\" value=\"#ffffff\" name=\"cardBg\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1-1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1-1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <div class=\"content-wrap\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                            Address</h2>\n                        <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                            <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">Creativity has always been one of the most powerful forces driving progress—whether it appears as a novel's delicate prose, a musician's haunting melody, a software developer's elegant code, or a designer’s signature style. Yet many creators only confront the legal side of creativity after they witness their work copied, misused, or exploited by someone else. That’s where understanding how copyright law protects your creative works becomes not only valuable, but essential.<br>\n<br>In today’s digital-first world, where content can spread globally in seconds, copyright law acts as a guardian for your originality. It ensures your ownership is recognized, your rights are enforceable, and your creative voice remains distinctly yours. Partnering with experienced professionals—such as a patent attorney or patent lawyer at Project Patent by Kaufhold and Dix Patent Law—can make navigating this landscape clearer, especially if your creative portfolio also touches adjacent areas like intellectual property, trademark law, or even the question of how to patent an idea.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"image-wrapper\">\n                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                           \n                        </div>\n                        <div class=\"image-wrap\">\n                            \n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_JSplaceholders": [],
          "_PHPplaceholders": [],
          "_anchor": "article04-2",
          "_isUserblock": true,
          "_cid": "v4vPga1c0V",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "_name": "header2",
          "_sourceTheme": "kidsm4",
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 15px)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 15px)",
              "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
                "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 5px)",
                "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 5px)"
              }
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            "img": {
              "width": "100%",
              "border-radius": "30px",
              "transform": "translate(1%, 5%)"
            },
            ".right-wrapper": {
              "padding-left": "5rem"
            },
            ".btn": {
              "padding": "0.7rem 2.4rem",
              "position": "relative"
            },
            ".container-fluid": {
              "max-width": "1200px",
              "padding": "0 1.4rem"
            },
            ".mbr-text": {
              "margin-top": "1.5rem",
              "margin-bottom": "2.5rem"
            },
            ".imageContainer": {
              "display": "inline-block",
              "position": "relative",
              "z-index": "0",
              "&:before": {
                "content": "''",
                "position": "absolute",
                "top": "0",
                "left": "0",
                "width": "96%",
                "height": "100%",
                "border": "2px dashed @warningColor",
                "border-radius": "30px",
                "z-index": "-1"
              }
            },
            ".btn:hover .inner-dashed-border": {
              "animation-play-state": "running"
            },
            "@keyframes dashed_border_running": {
              "100%": {
                "stroke-dashoffset": "-1000"
              }
            },
            ".svg1": {
              "position": "absolute",
              "padding": "2px",
              "rect": {
                "width": "~\"calc(100% - 4px)\"",
                "height": "~\"calc(100% - 4px)\""
              }
            },
            "@media (min-width: 767px) and (max-width: 992px)": {
              ".imageContainer": {
                "margin-bottom": "4.2rem"
              },
              ".right-wrapper": {
                "padding-left": "1.2rem"
              }
            },
            "@media (max-width: 767px)": {
              ".imageContainer": {
                "margin-left": "1rem",
                "margin-bottom": "3rem"
              },
              ".container-fluid": {
                "padding": "0 1rem"
              },
              ".right-wrapper": {
                "text-align": "center",
                "padding-left": "15px"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#000000"
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#000000"
            }
          },
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" group=\"Header\" class=\"header2 kidsm4_header2\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen, 'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n\t<mbr-parameters>\n\t\t\n\t\t<header>Size</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"15\" step=\"1\" value=\"10\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"15\" step=\"1\" value=\"11\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Left/Right Content\" name=\"reverse\">\n\t\t<header>Show/Hide</header>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Arrow\" name=\"showArrow\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubTitle\">\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n\t\t<header>Background</header>\n\t\t<fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/children.jpg\" parallax>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#dbffea\" selected>\n\t\t\t<input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/201169087\">\n\t\t</fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/children.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n\n\t\t<input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n\t\t<input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t<input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n\t\t\n\t</mbr-parameters>\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n\n\n\t<div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n\t<div class=\"container-fluid\">\n\t\t<div class=\"row\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverse}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-12 imageContainer\">\n\t\t\t\t<img src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/p1-pt-flatfee-608-608x416.jpg\" alt>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\n\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-12 col-lg-6 m-auto align-left right-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t<h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\"><b>Protecting Innovations with Project Patent by Kaufhold and Dix Patent Law</b></h1>\n\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"line-bg-primary\">Entertainment</span>\n\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t<p class=\"mbr-text mbr-light mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">Copyright law exists for a simple yet profound purpose: to safeguard the expression of your ideas. Unlike patents, which protect inventions, or trademarks, which secure brand identifiers, copyright shields artistic and intellectual creations—books, films, songs, artwork, architecture, software, choreography, photography, graphic design, and countless other expressions of creativity. What makes copyright so empowering is that these protections arise automatically the moment your work takes a tangible form. You don’t need to file anything, declare anything, or even publish the work.<br><br> Once it exists, the law protects it.\n<br>This automatic protection is just the beginning. Copyright gives you exclusive rights to reproduce, sell, license, publicly perform, distribute, and create derivative works from your creation. These rights give creators both control and economic opportunity. It ensures that when your work travels into the world—whether through a gallery wall, a streaming platform, a viral post, or even a corporate licensing deal—you are the one steering its purpose and receiving the credit and compensation it deserves.&nbsp;<br></p>\n\t\t\t\t<div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"button-svg mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"#\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Read More<svg fill=\"transparent\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"9 5\" stroke-dashoffset=\"0\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" class=\"wgl-dashes svg1 d-none inner-dashed-border animated-dashes\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<rect x=\"2px\" y=\"2px\" rx=\"25px\" ry=\"25px\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\"></rect>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</svg>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<div mbr-if=\"showArrow\" class=\"mbr-arrow hidden-sm-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n\t\t<a href=\"#next\">\n\t\t\t<i class=\"mbri-down mbr-iconfont\"></i>\n\t\t</a>\n\t</div>\n</section>",
