        {
          "_name": "article04",
          "_sourceTheme": "guidem5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article04 guidem5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"5\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Image\" name=\"showImage\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"BG\" value=\"#000000\" name=\"cardBg\" selected>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/guidem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@ADDONS_PATH@/guidem5/components/_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.8\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\">\n                <div class=\"image-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showImage\">\n                    <img class=\"large-radius\" src=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/what-is-considered-intellectual-property-infringement-in-colorado-1920x1080.jpg\" alt>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-8\">\n                <div class=\"card-wrapper large-radius\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showText || showButtons\">\n                    <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>How Copyright Interacts with Other Types of Intellectual Property</b></h2>\n                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">One of the biggest misconceptions creators have is that all rights protecting creative or innovative work fall under a single legal umbrella. In reality, the field of intellectual property includes distinct branches, each tailored to a different type of asset.<br><br> Understanding the borders between copyright, patents, and trademarks helps you avoid gaps in protection.\n<br>Copyright law protects expression—stories, music, artwork, software code.\n<br>Patent law protects inventions—mechanisms, processes, compositions of matter, and sometimes artistic innovations when they involve technology. This is where many creators begin exploring <a href=\"https://projectpatent.com/how-to-patent-an-idea\" class=\"text-primary\"><u>how to patent an idea</u></a> when their work involves unique functionality or technical originality.<br>\n<br>Trademark law protects brand elements—logos, slogans, colors, and other identifiers that anchor brand recognition.<br>\n<br>At Project Patent by Kaufhold and Dix Patent Law, clients benefit from a unified perspective on all three. Creative works rarely stay confined to one category. A software app, for instance, might involve copyrighted code, trademarked branding, and a patented algorithm. A designer’s product line might require both copyright and trademark strategies. And a filmmaker might need protection for scripts, names, logos, and digital assets.<br>\n<br>Recognizing how these forms of protection intersect ensures your creative ecosystem is fully defended—not just one part of it.&nbsp;<br></p>\n                        <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\">\n                            <a class=\"btn btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">\n                                <span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                                Read more\n                            </a>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
